<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="57">Notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="57">
<bibRefCitation author="Jordon, CTA" journalOrPublisher="Archives de la Flore de France et d'Allemagne" pageId="0" pageNumber="57" pagination="140 - 448" refId="B15" refString="Jordon, CTA, 1855. Notice sur plusieurs plantes novelles. Archives de la Flore de France et d'Allemagne 2: 140 - 448" title="Notice sur plusieurs plantes novelles." volume="2" year="1855">Jordon (1855)</bibRefCitation>
cited the following five collections: the Jura sur le Reculet (Ain), and Mont Ventoux, in August 1841, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="57">A. Jordan</emphasis>
; Mt. St-Nizier near Grenoble, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="57">Verlot</emphasis>
; Bex (canton of Vaud), 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="57">E. Thomas</emphasis>
; Mt. St-Nizier near Grenoble, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="57">Clement</emphasis>
. Also cited is a report of Reuter of his collection from Jura sur le Reculet [P-03161256, image!], and 
<taxonomicName class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Agrostis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Agrostis filiformis" order="Poales" pageId="0" pageNumber="57" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="filiformis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="57">Agrostis filiformis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
sensu 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="57">Vill</emphasis>
. We select The 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="57">Verlot 1584</emphasis>
specimen as there are several duplicates, and P-03161255 as the lectotype because that sheet is not mounted with any other collection as the MPU and BM sheets seem to be.
</paragraph>
